    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped basa</strong>, <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>spice paste</strong> to a bowl and mix thoroughly</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick), with a drizzle<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated</strong> <strong>basa </strong>and cook for an initial 1 min on each side</p>",
