    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and bring to the boil</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 3-4 min further or until the basa is cooked through, the liquid has evaporated, and the sauce is very thick – this is your <strong>Indonesian-style</strong> <strong>basa</strong> <strong>rendang</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
